                      "fill": "$text-primary",
                      "content": "各位小伙伴注意了！独库公路终于要在6月1日正式通车了！",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$text-md",
                      "fontWeight": "$weight-normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "iVbi5",
                      "name": "p2",
                      "fill": "$text-primary",
                      "content": "这条被誉为'中国最美公路'的天路，全长561公里，从独山子到库车，横穿天山山脉。一路上有雪山、草原、峡谷、戈壁，风景美到让人窒息。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$text-md",
                      "fontWeight": "$weight-normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "s9nop",
                      "name": "p3",
                      "fill": "$text-primary",
                      "content": "今年通车后新增了3个观景台，分别是：哈希勒根达坂观景台、铁力买提达坂观景台、大小龙池观景台。每个都能拍出大片！",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$text-md",
                      "fontWeight": "$weight-normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "noaqk",
                      "name": "p4",
                      "fill": "$text-primary",
                      "content": "划重点：6-8月是最佳通行时间，建议提前预约住宿，沿途住宿紧张。关注我，后续更新详细路书！",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": "$text-md",
                      "fontWeight": "$weight-normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
